直到上线亲手试用雷神的时候才知道我被代表了，我喜欢的角色特效被改成我不喜欢的角色特效。 我无意对以合理客观方式对官方提出修改意见的玩家们抱有恶意，因为我知道他们也是怀着提高自身游戏体验角度出发去反映自己想要改进的方面，但是，我彻彻底底地是无法忍受评论区里唇枪舌剑，得意洋洋的「修改后我很满意」的时候玩家，也看不惯那种不论自己立场如何但就是抱着一副高高在上的「反正就是我对」和「不爱玩你滚」的态度的玩家。 所以，我诚挚地向各位知乎的能人发问： 鉴于有人认为我在钓鱼，补上我雷神的图"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1b00f5cb641a8fe9c82be3e07f9adb00_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "115 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/492201795"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IlY3/jM/c8KgdEAMaCDcxNjU5NTI3IKncmosGMA84UUAccgk0OTIyMDE3OTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1634278120.0669541", "card_id": "Q_491815232", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "ShowMaker 在 S11 揭幕战上妖姬出门买长剑真是为了线权吗？有必要这样吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "不太理解，真的有必要用经济换普攻输出伤害吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a91ec816ffe35f624d0afc843b39a64e_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "107 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/491815232"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IlY3/jM/c8KgdEAMaCDcxNTczOTg5IPy7kIsGMAI4MEAdcgk0OTE4MTUyMzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1634278120.0675077", "card_id": "Q_491266095", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 380}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有没有人体验过《英雄联盟手游》但没继续玩下去？是什么原因弃坑了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-fb9511ee809c1e4ca9c168ac9f46a3e9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "100 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/491266095"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlY3/jM/c8KgdEAMaCDcxNDUxODgzIObfgIsGMAs4hgNAHnIJNDkxMjY2MDk1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "st